  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Villa Dirce’s built into the cliff above the town and it's the perfect place to enjoy some incredible views of Lake Garda. The centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c}" title="Limone">Limone</a> isn’t too far away – you can walk there in twenty minutes or hop on a shuttle bus which will get you there in minutes.</p>
<h2>Relaxing setting in Limone</h2>
<p>The hotel gardens are beautifully kept and you can smell the lemon trees as you walk around them. The rooms are all newly renovated and have a really fresh and comfortable feel. It's a great place to come back to after a busy day exploring the lake. The hotel is adults only (16 years and above) so it's a great place for relaxing and enjoying some peace and quiet!</p>]]></description>
