  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Superior Twin Rooms </strong>are between 15-18m² and sleep up to two people. Please request twin or double beds at the time of booking. These rooms are also available for sole use.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are around 30m² and sleep up to four people (extra bed is a double sofa bed). These rooms are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony or Terrace with lake views</li>
<li>Tea &amp; coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Air conditioning</li>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tax of approx. €1.50 per person per day is payable locally</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
